# Kodio Documentation (Writerside)

## Structure

Documentation lives in `kodio-docs/` as a JetBrains Writerside project. It is not included in `settings.gradle.kts` as a Gradle subproject, but it has a placeholder `build.gradle.kts`. Docs are built and deployed via `.github/workflows/docs.yml` to GitHub Pages on push to `master`.

## File Layout

```
kodio-docs/
├── topics/               # All documentation pages (flat directory)
├── images/               # Diagrams and assets (e.g. kodio-architecture.svg)
├── k.tree                # Table of contents / navigation tree
├── writerside.cfg        # Writerside project config
├── cfg/                  # Build profiles (buildprofiles.xml)
├── v.list                # Variables (version numbers, URLs)
├── c.list                # Custom elements
├── labels.list           # Reusable labels
├── redirection-rules.xml # URL redirects
└── build.gradle.kts      # Placeholder (docs are IDE/CI built)
```

